source.name: Comptroller--Annual Salaries as of March 5 2013
source.description: Annual salaries paid to employees by the Cook County Comptroller as ofMarch 5, 2013. Does not include deduction for furlough or closure days for employees subject to furloughs and closures. Does not include amounts paid by other governmental entities.
